# Payment Integration (Midtrans)

## Environment
- Dev/staging: Sandbox API (`https://api.sandbox.midtrans.com`)
- Production: hanya jika `MIDTRANS_IS_PRODUCTION=true`
- Keys di `.env.local`; **Server Key dilarang di client-side**

## Order & Stock
- Checkout: buat `Order` status `PENDING`, payment `PENDING`
- Kurangi stok saat order dibuat (lock stok)
- Auto-cancel order + restore stok jika tidak bayar dalam batas waktu Midtrans (~24 jam)

## Webhook (`/api/payment/notification`)
Verifikasi signature **sebelum** update DB:
```
SHA512(order_id + status_code + gross_amount + ServerKey)
```
Mismatch → `400 Bad Request`, abaikan request.

### Status Mapping
| Midtrans | Order |
|----------|-------|
| `capture` / `settlement` | payment `PAID`, status `PROCESSING` |
| `pending` | payment `PENDING` |
| `deny` / `cancel` / `expire` | payment `FAILED`, status `CANCELLED`, restore stok |

## Client Flow
- Midtrans Snap JS (sandbox: `https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/snap.js`)
- Prefer modal Snap, bukan redirect eksternal
- Setelah selesai/gagal → `/checkout/confirmation?orderId=...`
